outh/player.php?player=17295 |title=\u0414\u0436\u0435\u043d\u0435\u0442\u043e\u0432 \u041c\u0435\u0445\u0442\u0438 \u0420\u0430\u043c\u0430\u0437\u0430\u043d\u043e\u0432\u0438\u0447 |trans-title=Mehti Ramazanovich Dzhenetov |language=ru |date=29 September 2014 |access-date=29 September 2014 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140904214739/http://www.pfl-russia.com/competitions/season-2014-2015/south/player.php?player=17295 |archive-date=4 September 2014 |url-status=dead}}</ref>\n\nHe made his [[Russian Football National League]] debut for [[FC Anzhi Makhachkala]] on 30 May 2015 in a game against [[FC Sakhalin Yuzhno-Sakhalinsk]].\n\n==Career statistics==\n===Club===\n{{updated|match played 22 August 2018}}<ref>{{cite web |title=Mehdi C\u0259nn\u0259tov |url=https://int.soccerway.com/players/mehdi-cannatov/478278/ |website=soccerway.com |publisher=Soccerway |accessdate=4 August 2018 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180804110453/https://int.soccerway.com/players/mehdi-cannatov/478278/ |archive-date=4 August 2018 |url-status=dead}}</ref>\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align: center\"\n|+ Appearances and goals by club, season and competition\n|-\n!rowspan=\"2\"|Club\n!rowspan=\"2\"|Season\n!colspan=\"3\"|League\n!colspan=\"2\"|National Cup\n!colspan=\"2\"|Continental\n!colspan=\"2\"|Total\n|-\n!Division!!Apps!!Goals!!Apps!!Goals!!Apps!!Goals!!Apps!!Goals\n|-\n|rowspan=\"4\"|[[Sumgayit FK|Sumgayit]]\n|[[2016\u201317 Sumgayit FK season|2016\u201317]]\n|rowspan=\"3\"|[[Azerbaijan Premier League]]\n|0||0||0||0||colspan=\"2\"|-||0||0\n|-\n|[[2017\u201318 Sumgayit FK season|2017\u201318]]\n|5||0||4||0||colspan=\"2\"|-||0||0\n|-\n|[[2017\u201318 Sumgayit FK season|2017\u201318]]\n|2||0||0||0||colspan=\"2\"|-||0||0\n|-\n!colspan=\"2\"|Total\n!7!!0!!4!!0!!-!!-!!11!!0\n|-\n!colspan=\"3\"|Career total\n!7!!0!!4!!0!!-!!-!!11!!0\n|}\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n* {{Soccerway|mehdi-cannatov/478278|Mehdi C\u0259nn\u0259tov}}\n* {{Sportb